1 F. Student teaching and a prestudent teaching field experience
2 shall not be required of alternative placement program participants
3 for standard certification.
4 G. 1. The State Board of Education and the State Board of
5 Career and Technology Education shall promulgate rules authorizing
6 adjunct teachers who shall be persons with distinguished
7 qualifications in their field. Adjunct teachers shall not be
8 required to meet standard certification. A person employed as an
9 adjunct teacher pursuant to this subsection who does not hold a
10 valid certificate to teach shall not be considered a teacher as
11 defined by Section 1-116 of this title.
